_sText:
I remade all the maps that were so very special to me, changelog is as follows...

-CITYBRAWL (64 Players)
Optimized, nodraw + skybox.
Light added.

-OFFICERAMPAGE (40 Players)
Optimized.
Light added.
Added 2 new areas, Projector Room + Red Vent.
FishPool Room, Dead End, and Corner Office easier to barricade.

-LILA_OFF!CE (54 Players)
Optimized.
Light added.
Narrowed some doorways to easier barricade.
Took out 2 pipes in basement, added second shelf to side of cargo box + added metal shelf near white lights. This was all done to prevent cargobox stacking.

-OFFICEATTACK (68 Players)
Optimized.
Light added.
To prevent stair stacking added 1-2 new props in most barricade-able rooms.
More balanced.

All the maps were optimized, light added if they were fullbright + skybox in some maps for effects.
